    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王国落入疯王之手，他使用禁术试图让王后复活。但是，生与死的力量让他难以承受，结果，国王失去了理智。通过小心翼翼地击碎按钮，杀死成群的敌人！这款游戏忠实于格斗游戏，但又加入了策略元素，王国的命运就掌握在您的手中。每次闯关后，您都可以升级英雄兄弟会，解锁战斗技能、神器和英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369580/extras/590c16706498c88fe54afb317753ebf8.poster.avif?t=1770626108\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369580/extras/590c16706498c88fe54afb317753ebf8.webm?t=1770626108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369580/extras/590c16706498c88fe54afb317753ebf8.mp4?t=1770626108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们从深受玩家喜爱的经典游戏中汲取灵感，精心打造了一款将老式操作和复古感觉与创新 3D 机制相结合的beat'em'up 体验。游戏中的 4 个角色都有各自独特的战斗风格、影响游戏的自定义属性以及值得探索的详细背景故事。每个英雄都曾犯下罪恶。他们也需要救赎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369580/extras/1c4fbbed071d8468b58aa649230ba1a0.poster.avif?t=1770626108\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369580/extras/1c4fbbed071d8468b58aa649230ba1a0.webm?t=1770626108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369580/extras/1c4fbbed071d8468b58aa649230ba1a0.mp4?t=1770626108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ROGUELITE 进程 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次运行都会解锁新英雄、攻击招式和神器，同时在禁地回廊深处冒险，寻找疯王，让他从疯狂中解脱出来。每一次奔跑都是独一无二的，都有随机元素。只有团结一致的英雄兄弟才能战胜疯王：对疯王造成的任何伤害都会在同一次游戏中持续存在，直到所有英雄死亡或疯王被击败。在每次新的游戏中，所有英雄都会重生，但疯王也会恢复到完全健康状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369580/extras/f530031ce80614fac440dca598839949.poster.avif?t=1770626108\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369580/extras/f530031ce80614fac440dca598839949.webm?t=1770626108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369580/extras/f530031ce80614fac440dca598839949.mp4?t=1770626108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
